headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Capitalize on the Underground Arms Trade with Gunrunning Bonuses
content:
Boost your income as a Gunrunner in GTA Online this week and take advantage of a surplus of Bunker-related bonuses, including:

• 1.5X GTA$ and RP on Bunker Sell Missions
• 50% higher Bunker Stock Production and Bunker Research Speeds
• 30% off the Mobile Operations Center

If you're yet to get started on Gunrunning, head to the Maze Bank Foreclosures in-game site and buy a bunker.
